shows up for them is unique.

00:03:17.290 --> 00:03:20.980 align:middle line:84%
>> Using clairvoyance to obtain
verifiable information has been

00:03:20.980 --> 00:03:23.950 align:middle line:84%
repeatedly demonstrated in
the forms of remote viewing

00:03:23.950 --> 00:03:25.720 align:middle line:90%
and medical intuition.

00:03:25.720 --> 00:03:28.840 align:middle line:10%
The recent study at
IONS is the first design

00:03:28.840 --> 00:03:31.060 align:middle line:10%
to validate whether
clairvoyant seers are

00:03:31.060 --> 00:03:34.390 align:middle line:10%
able to accurately perceive
what occurs during an energy

00:03:34.390 --> 00:03:36.130 align:middle line:10%
medicine session.

00:03:36.130 --> 00:03:38.380 align:middle line:84%
It is a follow-up
to an earlier study

00:03:38.380 --> 00:03:41.830 align:middle line:84%
IONS did with the
participation of one seer which

00:03:41.830 --> 00:03:43.990 align:middle line:90%
yielded promising results.

00:03:43.990 --> 00:03:47.080 align:middle line:10%
As this experiment
incorporates multiple seers,

00:03:47.080 --> 00:03:50.080 align:middle line:10%
the researchers' hope is that
the findings will not only

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:52.420 align:middle line:10%
validate the practice
of clairvoyance

00:03:52.420 --> 00:03:57.160 align:middle line:10%
but will also shed light on
how energy medicine works.

00:03:57.160 --> 00:04:01.960 align:middle line:84%
>> And we had these Reiki
masters giving 30-minute

00:04:01.960 --> 00:04:04.840 align:middle line:84%
sessions to people who had a
variety of different health

00:04:04.840 --> 00:04:05.950 align:middle line:90%
conditions.

00:04:05.950 --> 00:04:11.110 align:middle line:84%
And in that space, we had
six clairvoyant seers who

00:04:11.110 --> 00:04:12.850 align:middle line:90%
were observing the sessions.

00:04:12.850 --> 00:04:15.100 align:middle line:84%
And the primary
research question

00:04:15.100 --> 00:04:20.310 align:middle line:84%
is, what is the corroboration
between those six

00:04:20.310 --> 00:04:25.180 align:middle line:84%
seers in terms of what they were
observing during each session?

00:04:25.180 --> 00:04:27.490 align:middle line:84%
Our hypothesis is
that there will

00:04:27.490 --> 00:04:30.310 align:middle line:84%
be a corroboration
between them, thus,

00:04:30.310 --> 00:04:37.390 align:middle line:84%
validating this experience
of clairvoyant seeing.

00:04:37.390 --> 00:04:40.750 align:middle line:84%
>> Researchers just finished
data collection and are working

00:04:40.750 --> 00:04:42.580 align:middle line:90%
on the findings.

00:04:42.580 --> 00:04:45.490 align:middle line:84%
In this study and others
being planned at IONS,

00:04:45.490 --> 00:04:48.280 align:middle line:84%
the goal is not only to
validate clairvoyance

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:52.670 align:middle line:84%
but also to understand
just how it works.

00:04:52.670 --> 00:04:57.850 align:middle line:10%
>> So this brings us to this
interesting paradigm shift that

00:04:57.850 --> 00:04:58.970 align:middle line:10%
we're in right now.

00:04:58.970 --> 00:05:02.980 align:middle line:84%
So we're moving from a
materialistic paradigm that

00:05:02.980 --> 00:05:06.850 align:middle line:84%
